<main class="pt-4">
    <!-- modal -->
    <div id="info-modal" tabindex="-1" class="modal modal-dialog-scrollable fade" style="display:none;" aria-labelledby="info-modal-label" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="modal-dialog">
            <div class="modal-content">
                <div class="modal-header">
                    <h5 class="modal-title" id="info-modal-label">Mode info</h5>
                    <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-body">
                    <p>In <code>2 creature mode</code>, you can type in the name of a different living organism in each box to learn the most specific taxonomy category that includes both.</p>
                    <p>In <code>1 creature 1 feature mode</code>, you can type in the name of an organism in the first box and any term or phrase in the second box to learn any facts about the organism that mention the feature in the second box.
                    <p>Note that, despite the use of the term "creature", the organism can be any 
                    <a href="https://species.wikimedia.org/wiki/Animalia" 
                        target="__blank" class="external-link">
                        Animalia<img class="external-icon" alt="(opens in new tab)" 
                            src="images/box-arrow-up-right.svg"></a>, 
                    <a href="https://species.wikimedia.org/wiki/Plantae" 
                        target="__blank" class="external-link">
                        Plantae<img class="external-icon" alt="(opens in new tab)" 
                            src="images/box-arrow-up-right.svg"></a>, 
                    <a href="https://species.wikimedia.org/wiki/Fungi" 
                        target="__blank" class="external-link">
                        Fungi<img class="external-icon" alt="(opens in new tab)" 
                            src="images/box-arrow-up-right.svg"></a>, 
                    <a href="https://species.wikimedia.org/wiki/Bacteria" 
                        target="__blank" class="external-link">
                        Bacteria<img class="external-icon" alt="(opens in new tab)" 
                            src="images/box-arrow-up-right.svg"></a>, 
                    <a href="https://species.wikimedia.org/wiki/Archaea" 
                        target="__blank" class="external-link">
                        Archaea<img class="external-icon" alt="(opens in new tab)" 
                            src="images/box-arrow-up-right.svg"></a>, or 
                    <a href="https://species.wikimedia.org/wiki/Protista" 
                        target="__blank" class="external-link">
                        Protista<img class="external-icon" alt="(opens in new tab)" 
                            src="images/box-arrow-up-right.svg"></a>.
                </div>
                <div class="modal-footer">
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" data-bs-dismiss="modal">Okay</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
    <form id="user-input-form" name="user-input-form" class="needs-validation" action="/results" method="post"  novalidate="novalidate"><!--aria-describedby="form-instructions"-->
        <div class="row mb-4">
            <label for="mode-selection" class="form-label col-auto m-0 pb-1">Mode:</label>
            <button type="button" id="info-btn" class="btn col-auto mb-1" aria-label="info button">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" role="img" aria-label="i icon" width="32" height="32" fill="green" class="bi bi-info-circle" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                  <path d="M8 15A7 7 0 1 1 8 1a7 7 0 0 1 0 14zm0 1A8 8 0 1 0 8 0a8 8 0 0 0 0 16z"/>
                  <path d="m8.93 6.588-2.29.287-.082.38.45.083c.294.07.352.176.288.469l-.738 3.468c-.194.897.105 1.319.808 1.319.545 0 1.178-.252 1.465-.598l.088-.416c-.2.176-.492.246-.686.246-.275 0-.375-.193-.304-.533L8.93 6.588zM9 4.5a1 1 0 1 1-2 0 1 1 0 0 1 2 0z"/>
                </svg>
            </button>
            <select id="mode_selection" name="mode_selection" class="form-select" aria-label="mode selection drop down">
                <option selected value="2-creature">2 creature mode</option>
                <option value="1-creature">1 creature 1 feature mode</option>
            </select>
        </div>
        <div class="row mb-4">
            <label for="searchbox_1" id="searchbox_1_label" class="form-label col-auto m-0 pb-1">creature 1:</label>
            <input id="searchbox_1" name="searchbox_1" type="search" spellcheck="true">
            <input id="searchbox_1_title" name="searchbox_1_title" value="" type="hidden">
        </div>   
        <div class="row mb-4">
            <label for="searchbox_2" id="searchbox_2_label" class="form-label col-auto m-0 pb-1">creature 2:</label>
            <input id="searchbox_2" name="searchbox_2" type="search" spellcheck="true">
            <input id="searchbox_2_title" name="searchbox_2_title" value="" type="hidden">
        </div>   
        <div class="row mb-4">
            <input type="submit" value="Submit"
                id="user-input-submit" name="user-input-submit" 
                class="btn btn-primary col-auto mb-1" aria-label="submit button">
        </div>   
    </form>
    </div>
</main>
{{> page/footer}}
{{> page/scripts}}
